body: They should of really put a "don't try this at home" tag on here. Read this while having breakfast earlier today and thought it looked like fun, so I took the hour drive to my parents house under the pretext of a normal visit. So I get there and exchange greetings and talk about all the normal stuff and they're asking me all the normal questions like "why don't you have a girlfriend yet" and "why are your pupils so big, are you on drugs". so eventually I get them to leave me alone and I go into my little sister's room. I walk up to her slap her chest and call her a flat bitch, but nothing happens, her chest doesn't grow at all. She just runs away crying. Next thing I know my father has stormed up the stairs yelling at me calling me a disgrace, saying mean things like "why do you always do things like this, we knew we should of aborted you". as I walk out the door he tells me not to come back till I've gotten the mental help that I need and then I leave.
what the fuvk

I'm sitting back at my place rn thinking over my actions and I realize what I did was wrong. I definitely didn't slap her chest hard enough which caused the spell or chemical reaction shown in this hmanga not to work. But I'm not going too give up. I shall keep experimenting with this till it works because if anime and hmanga ever taught me anything it's too never give up and too follow your dreams. Think I'm gonna go out and try this again on someone else now, wish me luck guys.
